# ⚙️ 13. CI/CD using GitHub Actions

Create file:

```
.github/workflows/ci.yml
```

```yaml
name: CI Pipeline

on:
  push:
    branches: [ "main" ]

jobs:
  build:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest

    steps:
    - uses: actions/checkout@v3

    - name: Setup Java
      uses: actions/setup-java@v3
      with:
        java-version: '17'

    - name: Build with Maven
      run: mvn clean install
```

