# ☸️ 16. Kubernetes Setup

Start Minikube:

```bash
minikube start
```

---

### deployment.yaml

```yaml
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: password-reset
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: reset
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: reset
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: reset
        image: yourusername/password-reset
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8080
```

---

### service.yaml

```yaml
apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: reset-service
spec:
  type: NodePort
  selector:
    app: reset
  ports:
    - port: 80
      targetPort: 8080
      nodePort: 30007
```

---

### Apply YAML

```bash
kubectl apply -f deployment.yaml
kubectl apply -f service.yaml
```

---

### Access App

```bash
minikube service reset-service
```

